text: "Somebody That I Used to Know" is a song written by Belgian-Australian singer- songwriter Gotye, featuring New Zealand singer Kimbra. The song was released in Australia and New Zealand by Eleven Music on 5 July 2011. It's second single from Gotye's third studio album, Making Mirrors (2011).
